Global Medium Chain Triglycerides(MCTs) Market Insights
Medium Chain Triglycerides(MCTs) Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Medium Chain Triglycerides (MCTs) Market Overview
The global Medium Chain Triglycerides (MCTs) market was valued at USD 1.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a significant CAGR of 7.5% from 2025 to 2030. MCTs are gaining popularity in the dietary supplement, food, and beverage industries due to their numerous health benefits, such as weight management and enhanced energy levels. The rise in health-conscious consumers, coupled with the increasing awareness about functional foods and natural ingredients, is driving the market demand. Additionally, the growing use of MCTs in ketogenic diets and sports nutrition products further contributes to the market's expansion.

